Class PhotosSearchController

java.lang.Object
photos.controllers.Controller
photos.controllers.PhotosSearchController
public class PhotosSearchController
extends Controller
Controller for the part of the normal-user subsystem that allows the user to search for photos using certain criteria
Author:
Robert Kulesa, Aaron Kan
